Interface RepartArtifact

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier

    public interface RepartArtifact
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Repart Artifact'. Rappresenta un artefatto all'interno di un modulo disponibile sul repository degli artefatti.

    The following features are supported:

    • Name
    • Type
